    title: 'Managing ART Side Effects: A Practical Guide for Long-term Wellness',
    excerpt: 'While modern HIV medications are much safer, some side effects can still occur. Learn how to identify and manage them effectively.',
    category: 'Treatment',
    author: 'Dr. Sophia Martinez',
